[2021-11-27 20:50:26 UTC] Papakatsu_: It's the angle link is at when he is shield surfing. The game stores this and only overwrites it when you bonk. The skew is activated when you shield surf forward and unequip your shield midair, causing link to snap to that angle and back again for a few frames. Although quick, the movement is just barely enough to clip through walls to get out of bounds. This is used to quickly finish trial of the sword and tests of strength with minimal fighting.
